items.title: 10 teens wounded in Queens mass shooting, police say

items.title: Details emerge about the victims of deadly New Orleans attack
items.description: At least 15 people were killed after a driver slammed into a crowd celebrating New Year's on Bourbon Street in New Orleans.

items.description: The 119th Congress begins Friday with Republicans in full control of the House and Senate for the first time since 2019. Here's what to know.

items.title: Gunman kills 12 people including 2 kids in Montenegro shooting spree
